      "task": "Explore the skill benchmark infrastructure in lisp/modules/ to understand Eight Keys scoring. SCOPE: Focus on gptel-benchmark-principles.el (primary) and gptel-skill-*.el (secondary, max 3 files). Provide a concise summary of how Eight Keys scoring works. List the 8 keys and their purpose.",
